SUMMARY: Understanding Your Child Through Their Personality Style
DESCRIPTION:Hello Friend\n\nAre you a Parent? Grand-Parent? Caregiver? Te
 acher or someone who is around children or grandchildren and want to unde
 rstand them better to have a smoother\, calmer relationship? I have devel
 oped a brand new series of workshops around Temperament/Personality Infor
 med knowledge that will be beneficial to many and I am super excited to s
 hare this information with you.\n\nI am running 60 minute pilot of “Under
 standing Your Child Through Their Personality Style” Workshop. It is offe
 red to you absolutely FREE.\n\nThis is an intro workshop and the insights
  can be helpful for all across generations - including toddlers\, tweens\
 , teens and adult children.\n\nDates and Times – (EST) Eastern Standard T
 ime – Toronto. Canada\n\nFebruary 18th Wednesday 7:30 pm (EST)\n\nFebruar
 y 20th Friday 11:00 am (EST)\n\nFebruary 22nd Sunday 2:00 (EST)\n\nIf you
  would like to attend\, please send me an e-mail with your First/Last nam
 e\, date and time you would like to attend at coach_niroma@yahoo.com mail
 to:coach_niroma@yahoo.com – I will forward you an invite with a Zoom Link
 \n\nPlease feel free to share this with others - If this can benefit anyo
 ne. Since it’s on ZOOM participants from other countries and time-zones c
 an also attend.
